<subSubSection pageId="71" pageNumber="555" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="71.[120,1330,1393,2216]" pageId="71" pageNumber="555">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[122,475,2064,2097]" pageId="71" pageNumber="555">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Vizotto’s Big-eyed bat is known from only ten individuals and virtually nothing is known about its diet, distribution, and life history.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
